title: Steele takes 2-shot lead into weekend at Silverado
text:
> Top News Steele takes 2-shot lead into weekend at Silverado A man watches the playing group of Ryo Ishikawa, of Japan, Whee Kim and D.H. Lee of South Korea, putt on the 10th green of the Silverado Resort North Course during the second round of the Frys.com PGA Tour golf tournament Friday, Oct. 16, 2015, in Napa, Calif. (AP Photo/Eric Risberg)
